基于在烂番茄([[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]])影评网上的三十四个影评，该电影有97%的好评。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10011295-samson_and_delilah/ | title=Samson and Delilah (review) | publisher=IGN Entertainment | work=Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate=11 August 2009 | archive-date=2020-09-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926101602/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10011295-samson_and_delilah | dead-url=no }}</ref>《赛门和黛利拉》在电视节目“上映电影”(At the Movie)中从玛格丽特﹒彭慕兰(Margaret Pomeranz)和大卫•斯特拉顿(David Stratton)那里收获了五星评价。这是唯一一部在2009年的节目中得到此评价的影片。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/atthemovies/txt/s2542612.htm|title=''Samson & Delilah'' (review)|publisher=[[ABC1|ABC]]: [[At_the_Movies_(Australian_TV_series)|At the Movies]]|accessdate=1 March 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140329131213/http://www.abc.net.au/atthemovies/txt/s2542612.htm|archive-date=2014-03-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.abc.net.au/atthemovies/review/byyear/2009.htm |title=Movie reviews, 2009 |publisher=[[ABC1|ABC]]: [[At_the_Movies_(Australian_TV_series)|At the Movies]] |accessdate=1 March 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140311082520/http://www.abc.net.au/atthemovies/review/byyear/2009.htm |archive-date=2014-03-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

